About YellowIpe
Our mission is to inspire the connection between technology and people, we foster the best of our professionals through our expertise in finding and attracting the best talent for the best projects. The Focus on People, Collaboration and Commitment are the pillars that guide us in this trajectory.
Join the yellow team as our new Senior Backend Engineer!
What You’ll Be Doing:
- Keep up-to-date with the latest web technologies, software architecture principles, and design patterns;
- Understand current workflows and contribute to the development of new lifecycles, prioritizing software quality processes;
- Take an active role in training and enhancing the skills of other web developers;
- Continuously monitor performance in production environments;
- Design and execute load tests while analyzing application performance;
- Develop our professional web-based application with a focus on dynamic interactions and responsive design;
- Build analytics dashboards and tools for web-based data visualization;
- Collaborate closely with our clinical team to define the optimal system workflow from the user's perspective.
What You Need To Have:
- Proven expertise in web development, with mandatory experience in Golang and/or NodeJS;
- Proficiency in SQL language and database management (familiarity with NoSQL databases is an advantage);
- Capability to write efficient, reusable, and high-performing code;
- Strong understanding of Software Engineering patterns, particularly in Web Services development;
- Experience with caching tools such as Memcached or Redis is a plus;
- Familiarity with continuous integration and deployment processes and related tools;
- Excellent communication skills, a proactive mindset, and problem-solving abilities;
- Solid written and technical English proficiency.
Location requirements:
- Remote - but candidates must reside in Portugal.
Apply for this opportunity in ourwebsite! =)
